Toby Huntington-Whiteley stars in the new summer advert for men's clothing brand Jacamo . 
  The personal trainer is joined by professional cricketer Freddie Flintoff for the campaign in Palma, Majorca . 
  Freddie has been the face of Jacamo for the last four years . 
  The 25-year-old is just under 6' 4' and models the latest collection of clothing . 
 